00037 #define DEBUG_SUBSYSTEM S_LNET
00038 
00039 #include "selftest.h"
00040 #include "console.h"
00041 
00042 enum {
00043         LST_INIT_NONE           = 0,
00044         LST_INIT_WI_SERIAL,
00045         LST_INIT_WI_TEST,
00046         LST_INIT_RPC,
00047         LST_INIT_FW,
00048         LST_INIT_CONSOLE
00049 };
00050 
00051 static int lst_init_step = LST_INIT_NONE;
00052 
00053 struct cfs_wi_sched *lst_sched_serial;
00054 struct cfs_wi_sched **lst_sched_test;
00055 
00056 static void
00057 lnet_selftest_exit(void)
00058 {
00059         int     i;
00060 
00061         switch (lst_init_step) {
00062                 case LST_INIT_CONSOLE:
00063                         lstcon_console_fini();
00064                 case LST_INIT_FW:
00065                         sfw_shutdown();
00066                 case LST_INIT_RPC:
00067                         srpc_shutdown();
00068                 case LST_INIT_WI_TEST:
00069                         for (i = 0;
00070                              i < cfs_cpt_number(lnet_cpt_table()); i++) {
00071                                 if (lst_sched_test[i] == NULL)
00072                                         continue;
00073                                 cfs_wi_sched_destroy(lst_sched_test[i]);
00074                         }
00075                         LIBCFS_FREE(lst_sched_test,
00076                                     sizeof(lst_sched_test[0]) *
00077                                     cfs_cpt_number(lnet_cpt_table()));
00078                         lst_sched_test = NULL;
00079 
00080                 case LST_INIT_WI_SERIAL:
00081                         cfs_wi_sched_destroy(lst_sched_serial);
00082                         lst_sched_serial = NULL;
00083                 case LST_INIT_NONE:
00084                         break;
00085                 default:
00086                         LBUG();
00087         }
00088         return;
00089 }
00090 
00091 void
00092 lnet_selftest_structure_assertion(void)
00093 {
00094         CLASSERT(sizeof(srpc_msg_t) == 160);
00095         CLASSERT(sizeof(srpc_test_reqst_t) == 70);
00096         CLASSERT(offsetof(srpc_msg_t, msg_body.tes_reqst.tsr_concur) == 72);
00097         CLASSERT(offsetof(srpc_msg_t, msg_body.tes_reqst.tsr_ndest) == 78);
00098         CLASSERT(sizeof(srpc_stat_reply_t) == 136);
00099         CLASSERT(sizeof(srpc_stat_reqst_t) == 28);
00100 }

00102 static int __init
00103 lnet_selftest_init(void)
00104 {
00105         int     nscheds;
00106         int     rc;
00107         int     i;
00108 
00109         rc = cfs_wi_sched_create("lst_s", lnet_cpt_table(), CFS_CPT_ANY,
00110                                  1, &lst_sched_serial);
00111         if (rc != 0) {
00112                 CERROR("Failed to create serial WI scheduler for LST\n");
00113                 return rc;
00114         }
00115         lst_init_step = LST_INIT_WI_SERIAL;
00116 
00117         nscheds = cfs_cpt_number(lnet_cpt_table());
00118         LIBCFS_ALLOC(lst_sched_test, sizeof(lst_sched_test[0]) * nscheds);
00119         if (lst_sched_test == NULL)
00120                 goto error;
00121 
00122         lst_init_step = LST_INIT_WI_TEST;
00123         for (i = 0; i < nscheds; i++) {
00124                 int nthrs = cfs_cpt_weight(lnet_cpt_table(), i);
00125 
00126                 /* reserve at least one CPU for LND */
00127                 nthrs = max(nthrs - 1, 1);
00128                 rc = cfs_wi_sched_create("lst_t", lnet_cpt_table(), i,
00129                                          nthrs, &lst_sched_test[i]);
00130                 if (rc != 0) {
00131                         CERROR("Failed to create CPT affinity WI scheduler "
00132                                "%d for LST\n", i);
00133                         goto error;
00134                 }
00135         }
00136 
00137         rc = srpc_startup();
00138         if (rc != 0) {
00139                 CERROR("LST can't startup rpc\n");
00140                 goto error;
00141         }
00142         lst_init_step = LST_INIT_RPC;
00143 
00144         rc = sfw_startup();
00145         if (rc != 0) {
00146                 CERROR("LST can't startup framework\n");
00147                 goto error;
00148         }
00149         lst_init_step = LST_INIT_FW;
00150 
00151         rc = lstcon_console_init();
00152         if (rc != 0) {
00153                 CERROR("LST can't startup console\n");
00154                 goto error;
00155         }
00156         lst_init_step = LST_INIT_CONSOLE;
00157         return 0;
00158 error:
00159         lnet_selftest_exit();
00160         return rc;
00161 }
